      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>I'm just so tired of being the one who always needs something. It feels like I'm just taking and taking from them. I look at them and I just see the stress and the way they have to change their whole lives just to make sure I'm okay. It doesn't feel right. It feels like I'm just making their lives harder by staying.",
